00:04:22.260 --> 00:04:24.260
me kete teknologji te Led-it,

00:04:24.260 --> 00:04:26.260
Llampa Led.

00:04:26.260 --> 00:04:28.260
Nje LED eshte nje semikonduktor. Eshte nje paisje elektronike.

00:04:28.260 --> 00:04:32.260
